race.comment: TARAWI LOCK (6) scored a 5.5 lengths win this course and distance last time in a personal Best Time (25.01) and also clocked one of the quickest wins on the card. In winning form and can measure up again. SIZZLE JACK (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (23.90) at Horsham latest. Comes through a solid form race last start. One of the better chances. RED BALL ROCKET (1) settled close the lead but was checked in the run and turned spotting a start, winding up strongly to score (22.58) at this track over 400m in a Mix 1/2/3. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. BLUE JUGGLER (7) racing over this course and distance brings the best out in him.
